Decent breakfast buffet, hot eggs and sausage or bacon, fresh melon and fruit along with your standard pastries and waffles.	Without everything else, it's your standard Quality Inn, and if you go in expecting that you'll be pleasantly surprised.	Considering the number of soulless chain hotels in the vicinity, this is a very good option if you're on a budget or you want something a little different.	Breakfast is included in the rate, standard fare but does the job.	The "continental" breakfast goes well beyond your standard bread and cereal breakfast.